  "prompt": "How can I get the mark-sheet transcripts from Jadavpur University?",
  "response": "To obtain your mark-sheet transcripts from Jadavpur University, follow these steps:\n\n1. **Visit the University Office:** Go to the examination section of the university, typically located on campus. The staff there will be able to guide you through the process.\n\n2. **Submit an Application:** You may be required to fill out an application form requesting your mark-sheet transcripts. This form can be obtained from the examination section or the university's official website.\n\n3. **Necessary Documents:** Ensure you have the required documents, which usually include:\n   - Your identity proof (e.g., student ID card, government-issued ID)\n   - Copies of previous mark-sheets or degrees\n   - Passport-size photographs (sometimes required)\n\n4. **Make the Payment:** There might be a fee associated with obtaining the transcripts. Ensure you are aware of the cost and the payment method accepted by the university.\n\n5. **Processing Time:** The university will inform you of the processing time for your transcripts. It can vary, so ensure you apply well in advance if you need them by a specific date.\n\n6. **Pickup or Delivery:** Depending on the university's policy, you might be able to collect the transcripts in person, or they may send them to your address. Confirm the mode of delivery during your application process.\n\n7. **Follow-ups:** If there are any delays or issues, regularly follow up with the examination section to ensure your request is being processed smoothly.\n\nFor detailed and updated information, it\u2019s best to directly contact the university administration or visit their official website.",
